  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.1-3r.ancient": "我不会借你船的。走开。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.STS_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA-S_T_S_KOMACHI_ONOZUKA.2-0r.ancient": "又在偷懒？",
